        "concept": "Two mute ghost-children who haunt the Stream, mouthing silent warnings.",
        "description": "<p>A pair of ghostly children who haunt the Stream, a few minutes from Stonetop near the base of the bluff. Sightings are uncommon, but common enough. They watch what happens at the water — seen or unseen — and manifest in silent terror, mouthing and gesturing at some danger, real or not.</p>",
